<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l34"><expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſneıd<ex>er</ex></expan> von mergentheim genant merıch . / vnd . C . hawſners vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l35">hannſen in der wog bey vns etc Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l36"><expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> . C . hawſner für des Reıchs gerıcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_145_r2l37">bey vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt / vnd hat begert vnd ſıch <expan>erbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein vnſchult </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_146" id="72r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l1">mıt <expan>ſein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> für dıe yncʒıcht dıe auf Jn gıeng daʒ er dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l2"><expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> . f . <expan>ſneıd<ex>er</ex></expan> gelt ſölt geſtoln oder <expan>abgetrage<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Daſſelb recht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l3">ıſt Jm auch erteylt vnd von Jm <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> / als denn des Reıchs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l4">gerıcht form vnd <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> bey vns ıſt . Jn des <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vns dennoch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l5">wol erfarn . daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> . C . <expan>hawſn<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>leẅmu<ex>n</ex>t</expan> bey vns ıſt wan wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l6"><expan>vb<ex>er</ex></expan> Jare genaıgt ſein / wo das an vns gelangt vntat ʒuſtraffen als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l7">vıl vns gebürt / Denn 
<del rend="strikethrough">von der klag <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> . f . <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l8">Als der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> . f . meynt daʒ Jn der hanns in der wog in <expan>eıne<ex>m</ex></expan> geleyt bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l9">vns v̈bel gehandelt ſüll <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . hat vns <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>meıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> geſagt als Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l10">der . f . das fürbrecht / do hab er Jm geantwurtt / er wölt <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l11"><expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> für vns <expan>beſend<ex>en</ex></expan> / da ſölt man ſein klag vnd des <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l12">wurt hören / vnd darcʒu tun als vns gebüret / des wölt der . f . <expan>ſneıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l13">niht harren / wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> / wıl <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> . f . <expan>ſneıd<ex>er</ex></expan> noch ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l14">denn <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> in der wog ıcht ʒu <expan>klag<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> klag vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l15">des <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> antwurt <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören vnd darnach darcʒu tun als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l16">vns gebürt / Deẅht Jn <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> . daʒ er <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu den <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l17">den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ıcht <expan>ʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett / ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheinbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l18">mıt <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſleẅnıgs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l19">Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / wenn wır des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> ſo <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l20">dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu den er <expan>ʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett bey vns anheim ſein ongeuerd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l21">Denn wo wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Otte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gedıene<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_146_r1l22">lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> margarete </ab>
